data.description: BELOW MARKET!!!! Cheap flood insurance $844 annually!!! Experience the ultimate waterfront lifestyle in this stunning 3 bedroom, 2 full bathroom, 2 car garage home on a saltwater canal with public water and sewer. Enjoy breathtaking views from your own private dock with a boat lift and seawall, while relaxing in your fully fenced backyard with a sparkling blue heated pool. This property is the epitome of luxury living with tall ceilings, foyer, formal living room, and a formal dining room perfect for entertaining guests. The large kitchen is equipped with solid surface counters, a dining nook, and a laundry room. The split floor plan ensures extra privacy, with the master suite featuring dual walk-in closets that lead to the large master bathroom. Here, you'll find dual vanities with ample storage, a make-up vanity, a soaking tub, a walk-in shower, and a big window that lets in plenty of natural light. You'll appreciate the high-end finishes throughout the home, with tile in the living areas and luxury vinyl in the bedrooms, ensuring a seamless look and feel. The outside of the home has undergone significant updates, including a 2023 shingle roof, 2022 fence, 2021 HVAC, RV outlet and 2023 dock decking, power and water at dock, making this property truly move-in ready. This home is located in South Gulf Cove, a sought-after waterfront community that offers optional HOA amenities. Take advantage of the community's prime location, just minutes away from shopping, dining, and some of Florida's finest beaches. Don't miss your chance to own this waterfront beauty. Schedule a tour today!
